quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  8,65,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU HERRIDIL-MU’UMININE ‘ALEL-KITALI ‘IN JEKUN MINKUM ‘ISHRUNE SABIRUNE JEGLIBU MIA’ETEJNI WE ‘IN JEKUN MINKUM MIA’ETUN JEGLIBU ‘ELFÆN MINEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BI’ENNEHUM KAWMUN LA JEFKAHUNE
  8,66,EL-’ANE HAFFEFEL-LAHU ‘ANKUM WE ‘ALIME ‘ENNE FIKUM DA’FÆN FE’IN JEKUN MINKUM MIA’ETUN SABIRETUN JEGLIBU MIA’ETEJNI WE ‘IN JEKUN MINKUM ‘ELFUN JEGLIBU ‘ELFEJNI BI’IDHNI ELLAHI WEL-LAHU ME’A ES-SABIRINE
  8,67,MA KANE LINEBIJIN ‘EN JEKUNE LEHU ‘ESRA HETTA JUTHHINE FIL-’ERDI TURIDUNE ‘AREDE ED-DUNJA WEL-LAHU JURIDUL-’AHIRETE WEL-LAHU ‘AZIZUN HEKIMUN
  8,68,LEWLA KITABUN MINEL-LAHI SEBEKA LEMESSEKUM FIMA ‘EHADHTUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  8,69,FEKULU MIMMA GANIMTUM HELALÆN TEJJIBÆN WE ETTEKU ELLAHE ‘INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN